Note on the MCP service:

This MIT license covers only the plugin source code in this directory
(SKILL.md files, plugin manifest, commands, documentation). The
`aria` MCP server at https://www.patchline.ai/api/mcp/v2 is a
Patchline-hosted proprietary service. Calling it requires a Patchline AI
account and Cognito OAuth authentication. Forking this plugin does not
grant access to the MCP service; you'll need a Patchline account just
like any other user.

This pattern — open-source client code + authenticated paid service —
matches the AWS, OpenAI, and Anthropic SDK model.
